    "Results highlight the model's difficulty in managing additional annotation complexity.",
    "C. Insight GenerationAmong all 160 tasks, after self-debugging, 134 successfully generated insight text content that provided some level of analysis of the tasks.",
    "However, among these, 18 did not generate the insight in the required JSON format.We conducted a statistical analysis to compare the success rates of generating each key-value pair in the standardized insight dictionaries.To generate the insights, we employed two different approaches.",
